### Basic Weather Service (Backward Compatible)
GET https://localhost:7002/api/weather?lat=51.5&lon=-0.1&service=openmeteo

### Advanced Weather Service with Factory Pattern
POST https://localhost:7002/api/weather/advanced?lat=51.5&lon=-0.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "environment": "production",
  "region": "europe",
  "requiresAuthentication": false,
  "enableCaching": true,
  "enableRetryPolicy": true,
  "customTimeoutSeconds": 30,
  "customUserAgent": "MyWeatherApp/2.0",
  "requiredFeatures": ["current_weather", "forecast"]
}

